{"tid":232792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[邪門玩意] 淘寶攝影器材匯報區 (2)","createTime":"2017-05-07T05:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T05:13:01.000Z","uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbca74db48a7287cad098367c0999b8b5c5a29a2","tid":232792,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"幫巴打開新post <br />\n<blockquote>各位巴打，又係我呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;<br />\n上次係舊台出過一次淘寶攝影器材交流Post&hellip;<br />\n今次到左新台都開返個同大家交流下&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n首先淘寶野未必係講共產既貨&hellip;會有外國野、或二手鏡之類<br />\n所以大家唔好以為得共產野！<br />\n<br />\n而我每次行星際行睇實辦時，都見好多巴打買配件之類既野，其實星際有既淘寶大部份都會有，所以大家可以係星際睇左實樣後上淘寶，價錢方面應該會有驚喜&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n等我匯報第一件野：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u6oweq12\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu6oweq12&h=e4a2c4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ikxcde16\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fikxcde16&h=8da6530d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aw187p34\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faw187p34&h=e165720b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我依隻係舊款買左80人仔（已經無貨）<br />\n<br />\n新款既就下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xrcnu059\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxrcnu059&h=bcfc93f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家發問同參與！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"87683b94dd2526c77aec111490db3da172a2ecfb","tid":232792,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無人識係阿里巴巴買野?<br />\n我見d野價錢好平，仲寫到明買幾多就平幾多<br />\n我係1688搵到支GA157T &yen;580<br />\n淘寶一般賣緊 &yen;665<br />\n但係1688買野佢要用大陸卡唔可以用香港信用卡比錢<br />\n最後賣家比左係淘寶既鋪頭link我買做翻1688個價<br />\n有無巴打有無方法直接係1688買野??</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://uploads.im/4iJOU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fuploads.im%2F4iJOU.png&h=8ffdf576&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u3w9f7qj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu3w9f7qj&h=9727b3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1688一般係做批發畀舖頭入貨用，有支付寶會方便好多。</blockquote><br />\n佢d價錢好吸引，但用唔到香港visa比錢</blockquote><br />\n用1688個價係淘寶買左喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rnOgNxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrnOgNxX.jpg&h=dc790049&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f0b42f43bbfa4842896ab7356b06417292be47a","tid":232792,"uid":70497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"單反自拍掍，有冇介紹？"},{"pid":"a1594b3dfd160aeccea1e7382c1c9f21b30c6083","tid":232792,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"屌，錯台請del"},{"pid":"6923879053c761e080254a763dde8bad04f2ff85","tid":232792,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"錯台，請去下面個post<br />\n[邪門玩意]淘寶攝影器材匯報區 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/232796/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/232796/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}